  m_text: This will let you choose if the bots are visible or not. Great for<br>practicing
    the mechanic without relaying on them for your own position.<br><br>- <b>Hide
    Characters</b> means that only the nameplate and model of the bots are hidden.<br><br>-
    <b>Completely Hidden</b> means that everything regarding the bots are hidden,<br>no
    tether visuals, no debuff visuals, nothing. This setting can make some timelines<br>incredibly
    difficult or impossible to do correctly. Try it out yourself to see how it is.
